--- title: "Proceso Electoral 2018" css: custom.css --- ## Proceso Electoral 2018: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} library(tidyverse) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` ── Attaching core tidyverse packages ──────────────────────── tidyverse 2.0.0 ── ✔ dplyr 1.1.4 ✔ readr 2.1.5 ✔ forcats 1.0.0 ✔ stringr 1.5.1 ✔ ggplot2 3.5.1 ✔ tibble 3.2.1 ✔ lubridate 1.9.3 ✔ tidyr 1.3.1 ✔ purrr 1.0.2 ── Conflicts ────────────────────────────────────────── tidyverse_conflicts() ── ✖ dplyr::filter() masks stats::filter() ✖ dplyr::lag() masks stats::lag() ℹ Use the conflicted package () to force all conflicts to become errors ``` ::: ```{.r .cell-code} library(readxl) library(reactable) options(scipen=999) options(digits=2) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018 <- read_excel("C:/Users/Eduardo/Documents/PC/SECCION1/DOCS/Tesis/FEDERAL/senado 2018.xlsx") reactable(senfed2018) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018 <- senfed2018%>% select(-ID_DISTRITO, -CABECERA_DISTRITAL, -SECCIONES , -CASILLAS , -TRIBUNAL, -JUICIO, -OBSERVACIONES, -RUTA_ACTA) reactable(senfed2018) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018 <- senfed2018%>% rename(NUAL = 'NA') reactable(senfed2018) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Manipulación de Datos: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018 <- senfed2018%>% select(-NUM_VOTOS_CAN_NREG)%>% gather(key = Partido, value = Votos, PAN:CAND_IND7) reactable(senfed2018) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Agrupaciones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_1 <- senfed2018%>% group_by(ID_ESTADO, NOMBRE_ESTADO, Partido)%>% reframe(Votos = sum(Votos), LISTA_NOMINAL = sum(LISTA_NOMINAL), TOTAL_VOTOS = sum(TOTAL_VOTOS), NUM_VOTOS_NULOS = sum(NUM_VOTOS_NULOS))%>% arrange((ID_ESTADO)) reactable(senfed2018_1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_1 <- senfed2018_1[!is.na(senfed2018_1$Votos),] reactable(senfed2018_1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Agrupaciones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} suma_F2018S <- senfed2018_1%>% group_by(ID_ESTADO, NOMBRE_ESTADO)%>% reframe(Votos1 = sum(Votos)) reactable(suma_F2018S) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Uniones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_1_f <- senfed2018_1 %>% left_join(suma_F2018S, by = c("ID_ESTADO", "NOMBRE_ESTADO")) reactable(senfed2018_1_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_1_f <- senfed2018_1_f%>% mutate(Proporcion= (Votos/Votos1)*(100)) reactable(senfed2018_1_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Agrupaciones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_2_f <- senfed2018_1_f%>% group_by(Partido)%>% reframe(sum(Votos), sum(Proporcion/32)) reactable(senfed2018_2_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_2_f <- senfed2018_2_f%>% rename(Votos = `sum(Votos)`, Proporcion = `sum(Proporcion/32)`) reactable(senfed2018_2_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_2_f <- senfed2018_2_f%>% mutate(Partido = ifelse(Partido == "NUAL", "Otro", Partido))%>% mutate(Partido = ifelse(Partido == "ES", "PES", Partido)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} reactable(senfed2018_2_f) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integantes_senado <- read_excel("C:/Users/Eduardo/Documents/PC/SECCION1/DOCS/Tesis/Integrantes/Integrantes_senado.xlsx") reactable(integantes_senado) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integantes_senado <- integantes_senado%>% mutate(Partido = ifelse(Partido == "morena", "MORENA", Partido))%>% mutate(Partido = ifelse(Partido == "Movimiento Ciudadano", "MC", Partido)) ``` ::: ### Agrupaciones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integantes_senado_1 <- integantes_senado%>% group_by(Partido, Sexo)%>% count() reactable(integantes_senado_1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} integantes_senado_1 <- integantes_senado_1%>% mutate(Partido = ifelse(Partido == "SG", "Otro", Partido)) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} reactable(integantes_senado_1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ### Uniones: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_2_f1 <- senfed2018_2_f%>% inner_join(integantes_senado_1, by= "Partido") reactable(senfed2018_2_f1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
``` ::: ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} senfed2018_2_f1 <- senfed2018_2_f1%>% rename(Curules = `n`) ``` ::: ### Presentación del Tibble: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} reactable(senfed2018_2_f1) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
